OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FThe cast for the new series of the
OL,7,Ficonic Jersey detective drama Bergerac
OL,8,Fhas been announced by British
OL,9,Fbroadcaster UKTV.
OL,11,FDamien Molony takes on the leading
OL,12,Frole of Jim Bergerac - he has
OL,13,Fpreviously appeared in shows such as
OL,14,FBrassic, The Split and Derry Girls.
OL,16,FThe Irish actor follows in the
OL,17,Ffootsteps of John Nettles who played
OL,18,Fthe troubled Detective Sergeant during
OL,19,Fthe programme's original run from 1981
OL,20,Fto 1991.
