OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FMore than 30 years on, Damien says:
OL,7,F"I'm incredibly excited to be stepping
OL,8,Finto the role. John Nettles has left
OL,9,Fan incredible legacy with big shoes to
OL,10,Ffill and I hope I can bring a fresh
OL,11,Ftake on this iconic character."
OL,13,FHe will be joined by acclaimed actor
OL,14,FZoe Wanamaker, perhaps best known for
OL,15,Fher appearances in My Family and Harry
OL,16,FPotter, and Philip Glenister from Life
OL,17,Fon Mars and Ashes to Ashes.
OL,19,FZoe will play Bergerac's mother-in-law
OL,20,FCharlie Hungerford and Philip is
OL,21,FArthur Wakefield.
