OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FOther cast members include Pippa
OL,7,FHaywood, Robert Gilbert, Sasha Behar
OL,8,Fand Celine Arden.
OL,10,FUnlike the original which tackled a
OL,11,Fnew storyline for each episode, the
OL,12,Fremake will see one mystery run across
OL,13,Fthe series.
OL,15,FShowmakers want to honour Bergerac's
OL,16,Fhistory with a contemporary twist and
OL,17,Fsay viewers will be reintroduced to
OL,18,Fhim as a broken man, dealing with
OL,19,Fgrief and alcoholism after his wife's
OL,20,Fdeath.
