OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,FWhen a woman from a rich Jersey family
OL,7,Fis murdered, Jim must deal with his
OL,8,Fpersonal struggles as he tries to
OL,9,Fcrack the case.
OL,11,FThe island's tourist board Visit
OL,12,FJersey has put its support behind the
OL,13,Frebooted show, with Chief Executive
OL,14,FTricia Warwick saying: "For many, the
OL,15,Fwords 'Jersey' and 'Bergerac' are
OL,16,Fsynonymous and we are delighted for
OL,17,Fthe iconic TV series to return to our
OL,18,Fisland's beautiful shores.
