OL,3,CStar-studded cast announced for new
OL,4,CBergerac TV series
OL,6,F"The modern re-imaging presents an
OL,7,Fopportunity to celebrate the show's
OL,8,Flegacy in Jersey, whilst reaching a
OL,9,Fnew generation of fans who will be
OL,10,Feager to 'jet set' to the featured
OL,11,Flocations."
OL,13,FFilming is due to begin in July and
OL,14,Fwill include locations in Jersey and
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,FThe show will air across six episodes
OL,18,Ffor free on UKTV channel U&DRAMA and
OL,19,Fonline streaming service U in 2025.
